Class Job

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.sched.Job
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Job>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ActionPlanJob, ArchiveSamplesJob, CreateCorridorsJob, DeviceActionJob, EventPurgeJob, FlushSamplesJob, FlushXmlJob, FutureOp, IncidentXmlJob, MeteringJob, ParkingAreaJob, ProfilingJob, ReaperJob, SendSettingsJob, SignMessageXmlJob, TimeActionJob, TollZoneJob, WeatherSensorXmlJob, XmlConfigJob
public abstract class Job extends Object implements Comparable<Job>
Job for the scheduler to perform. When the scheduler is ready, the perform method is called. The perform method must be implemented by any subclasses.
Author:
Douglas Lau
